- 내일 5일(목) 2학년은 온라인수업, 1,3학년은 등교
- 수업교재가 학교에 있어도 학교와서 가져가지 말고 적절히 수업에 임하기
- 방역지침을 준수하고 강화하기(마스크,손소독하기, 외출하지 않기)
- 항상 비상연락받을 수 있도록 잘 대기

[홍함바퀴둘러서공중부양] [오후 8:51] 충남아산FC는 2020년 새롭게 창단한 구단입니다.

기존에는  체육단에서 군복무하는 의경 선수들을 대상으로 운영됐던 클럽이지만

 의경 체육단이 폐지됨에 따라 새롭게 시민구단으로 창단한 구단입니다. 

​

아산 무궁화 프로축구단 시절에도 꾸준한 CSR 활동을 해온 아산은 시민구단이 된 지금도 열심히 CSR 활동에 참여하고 있습니다.

2017년 창단과 함께 꾸준히 CSR 활동을 해왔고

경찰팀과 일반 선수들이 함께 뛰는 혼용구단 시절인 2019년에는 목표로 세운 CSR 100회를 달성했습니다. 

​

시민구단으로 전환된 지금은 더욱 CSR 활동에 박차를 가하고 있습니다. 

특히 기존 스쿨어택과 지역 어린이들에게 축구 교육은 물론, 올해 지역민들이 수해로 고생하자 수해복구를 위해 직접 봉사활동에 참여했습니다. 

더불어 코로나 19를 극복하고자, '2020 함께 걷는 안산 마스크 기부 캠페인'을 진행하여 큰 화제를 모았습니다.

[홍함바퀴둘러서공중부양] [오후 3:21] 안녕하세요 *알바천국* 보고 연락드려요^^

의정부경전철역,의정부역에 위치한 간단한 보드게임을 하며 대화하는 컨셉의 대화형 보드카페입니다.
사업자등록증이 정식으로 있는 업체입니다.

★저희는 정말로 전혀 터치 없이 떨어져 마주 앉아서 오직 대화만 하시면서 일하시는게 가능합니다.★
정확한 사실이고 아무런 부담없이 해보실 수 있는 일 입니다!!

술 마시는 업종 아닙니다..가게에 술 자체가 없어용.

시급은 최저 30,000원 부터 70,000원까지 입니다.
당연히 페이는 퇴근하실 때 전액 당일 현금으로 지급해 드립니다.
(본인의 꿈을 이루기 위한 과정에 꼭 필요한 돈을 벌어가세요~)

영업시간도 오전 9시부터 새벽 02시까지라서 낮 근무가 가능합니다.

직원의 불규칙한 근무시간도 업종 특성상 아무 상관이 없습니다.
매일 나오셔도 되고 일주일에 한번 나오셔도 됩니다.
주중에만 나오셔도 되고 주말에만 나오셔도 됩니다.
출근하셔서 일하시는 시간대와 길이도 자유입니다.
(출근 전날 "저 내일 몇시출근 몇시퇴근 할게요" 라고 말씀만 주시면 됩니다.^^)

한두 시간 일해보시고 근무 결정하셔도 됩니다.
그 부분도 시급은 당일 현금 지급해드립니다.~

궁금하신 점 있으시면 언제든 편하게 이번호로 문자 또는 전화주세용.
자세하게 설명드릴게요.
카톡아이디는 schedule7 입니다.

혹시나 이렇게 연락드린 게 불편하셨다면 정말 정말 죄송합니다.ㅠㅠ
긴 글 읽어주셔서 감사합니다.

[홍함바퀴둘러서공중부양] [오후 11:31] module  ir_rx(
    output reg  [31:0]  o_data,
    output reg  [1:0]   state,
    input               i_ir_rxb, 
    input               i_clk,
    input               i_rstn
);

    localparam  IDLE        = 2'b00 ;
    localparam LEADCODE     = 2'b01 ; // 9ms high 4.5ms low
    localparam DATACODE     = 2'b10 ; // Custom & Data Code
    localparam  COMPLETE    = 2'b11 ;   // 32-bit data

    //  Generate 1MHZ Clock
    wire            clk_1M;
    nco u_nco( 
        .o_clk      (clk_1M ),
        .i_num      (50     ),
        .i_clk      (i_clk  ),
        .i_rstn     (i_rstn ));

    // Sequential Rx Bits
    wire            ir_rx;
    assign          ir_rx = ~i_ir_rxb;

    reg     [1:0]   seq_rx          ;
    always @(posedge clk_1M or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            seq_rx <= 2'b00; 
        end else begin
            seq_rx <= {seq_rx[0], ir_rx}; 
        end
    end

    //  Count Signal Polarity (High & Low)
    reg [15:0] cnt_h            ;
    reg [15:0] cnt_l            ;
    always @(posedge clk_1M or negedge i_rstn) begin 
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            cnt_h <= 16'd0; 
            cnt_l <= 16'd0;
        end else begin 
            case(seq_rx)
                2'b00   : cnt_l <= cnt_l + 1; 
                2'b01   : begin
                    cnt_l <= 16'd0; 
                    cnt_h <= 16'd0;
                end
                2'b11   : cnt_h <= cnt_h + 1; 
            endcase
        end 
    end

    // State Machine 
    //reg [1:0] state     ;
    reg [5:0] cnt32     ;
    
    always @(posedge clk_1M or negedge i_rstn) begin 
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            state <= IDLE;
            cnt32 <= {6{1'b1}};
        end else begin
            case (state)
                IDLE: begin
                    state <= LEADCODE; 
                    cnt32 <= {6{1'b1}};
                end
                LEADCODE: begin
                    if (cnt_h >= 8500 && cnt_l >= 4000) begin 
                        state <= DATACODE;
                    end else begin
                        state <= LEADCODE;
                    end 
                end
                DATACODE: begin
                    if (seq_rx == 2'b01) begin 
                        cnt32 <= cnt32 + 1;
                    end else begin
                        cnt32 <= cnt32;
                    end
                    if (cnt32 == 32) begin 
                        state <= COMPLETE;
                    end else begin
                        state <= DATACODE;
                    end 
                end
                COMPLETE: state <= IDLE;
                endcase
            end
        end

    //      32bit Custom & Data Code 
    reg     [31:0]  data        ;
    always @(posedge clk_1M or negedge i_rstn) begin 
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            data <= 0;
        end else begin
            case (state)
                DATACODE: begin
                    if (cnt_l >= 1000) begin 
                        data[31-cnt32] <= 1;
                    end else begin 
                        data[31-cnt32] <= 0;
                    end 
                end
                COMPLETE: o_data <= data;
            endcase 
        end
    end
   
endmodule

module signal_integration(
    output reg [7:0]        o_signal_data,
    input      [1:0]        i_now_state,
    input     [31:0]        i_data,
    input                   i_clk,
    input                   i_rstn
);
    localparam IDLE             = 2'b00 ;
    localparam SIG_MODE_CLOCK   = 32'hFDA05F; //^버튼 누름 (0번-SIG_MODE_CLOCK, 1번-SIG_MODE_SETUP, 2번-SIG_MODE_ALARM, 3번-SIG_MODE_TIMER)
    localparam POS_SELECT       = 32'hFD40BF; // MENU버튼 누르면 분 부분 선택, 누르지 않으면 초 부분이 선택됨(기본값)
    localparam SIG_PLUS         = 32'hFD20DF; // +버튼 누르면 증가(기본값)
    localparam SIG_MINUS        = 32'hFD30CF; // -버튼 누르면 +버튼이 감소 버튼으로 바뀜
    localparam TIMER_ONOFF      = 32'hFD906F; // OK버튼 누르면 TIMER ON
    localparam ALARM_ONOFF      = 32'hFD10EF; // <버튼 누르면 ALARM ON

    always@(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn)begin
        if(!i_rstn)begin
            o_signal_data <= 8'b11111111;
        end else begin
            if(i_now_state!=IDLE)begin
                o_signal_data <= 8'b11111111;
            end else begin
                case(i_data)
                    SIG_MODE_CLOCK: begin           // i_data가 SIG_MODE_CLOCK인 경우
                        o_signal_data[0]<=1'b0; 
                        o_signal_data[1]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[2]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[3]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[4]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[5]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[6]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[7]<=1'b1;
                    end
                    POS_SELECT: begin               // i_data가 POS_SELECT인 경우
                        o_signal_data[0]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[1]<=1'b0;
                        o_signal_data[2]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[3]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[4]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[5]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[6]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[7]<=1'b1;
                    end
                    SIG_PLUS: begin                 // i_data가 SIG_PLUS인 경우
                        o_signal_data[0]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[1]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[2]<=1'b0; 
                        o_signal_data[3]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[4]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[5]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[6]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[7]<=1'b1;
                    end
                    SIG_MINUS: begin 
                        o_signal_data[0]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[1]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[2]<=1'b1; 
                        o_signal_data[3]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[4]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[5]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[6]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[7]<=1'b0;
                    end
                    TIMER_ONOFF: begin 
                        o_signal_data[0]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[1]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[2]<=1'b1; 
                        o_signal_data[3]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[4]<=1'b0;
                        o_signal_data[5]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[6]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[7]<=1'b1;
                    end
                    ALARM_ONOFF: begin 
                        o_signal_data[0]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[1]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[2]<=1'b1; 
                        o_signal_data[3]<=1'b0;
                        o_signal_data[4]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[5]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[6]<=1'b1;
                        o_signal_data[7]<=1'b1;
                    end
                     default: begin
                        o_signal_data <= 8'b11111111;// 다른 경우에 대한 처리, 필요에 따라 추가
                    end
                endcase
            end
        end
    end
endmodule


module nco(
    output reg      o_clk,
    input   [31:0]  i_num,
    input           i_clk,
    input           i_rstn
);
    reg [31:0] cnt;
    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            cnt     <= {32{1'b0}};
            o_clk   <= 0;
        end else begin
            if(cnt >= i_num/2 - 1) begin
                cnt     <= 0;
                o_clk   <= ~o_clk;
             end else begin
                cnt     <= cnt + 1;
                o_clk   <= o_clk;
            end
        end
    end
endmodule

module cnt_param#(
    parameter RANGE = 60
)(
    output reg  [$clog2(RANGE)-1:0]     o_cnt,
    input                               i_direct,
    input                               i_clk,
    input                               i_rstn
);
    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            if(!i_direct) begin
                o_cnt   <= {$clog2(RANGE){1'b1}};
            end else begin
                o_cnt   <= RANGE;
            end
        end else begin
            if(!i_direct) begin
                if(o_cnt == RANGE-1) begin
                    o_cnt   <= 0;
                end else begin
                    o_cnt   <= o_cnt + 1;
                end
            end else begin
                if(o_cnt == 0) begin
                    o_cnt   <= RANGE-1;
                end else begin
                    o_cnt   <= o_cnt - 1;
                end
            end
        end
    end
endmodule

module led_ctrl#(
    parameter   NCO_LED_SPEED = 50
)(
    output reg  [6:0]       o_seg,
    output reg              o_seg_dp,
    output reg  [5:0]       o_seg_enb,
    input       [6*7-1:0]   i_six_seg,
    input       [5:0]       i_six_seg_dp,
    input       [1:0]       i_mode,     // 추가
    input                   i_timer_mode,  //추가
    input       [1:0]       i_position, // 추가
    input                   i_clk,
    input                   i_rstn
);
    wire                    clk_disp_speed;
    nco u_nco(
        .o_clk      (clk_disp_speed ),
        .i_num      (NCO_LED_SPEED  ),
        .i_clk      (i_clk          ),
        .i_rstn     (i_rstn         ));
    wire    [2:0]   cnt_seg_enb;
    cnt_param#(
        .RANGE      (6              ))
    u_cnt_param(
        .o_cnt      (cnt_seg_enb    ),
        .i_direct   (1'b0           ),
        .i_clk      (clk_disp_speed ),
        .i_rstn     (i_rstn         ));

    wire clk_2Mhz;
    nco u_nco_5hz (
        .o_clk      (clk_2Mhz       ),
        .i_num      (25             ), // 블링크 속도 설정
        .i_clk      (i_clk          ),
        .i_rstn     (i_rstn         ));

    reg     [48:0]      blink_counter   = 0;
    reg                 display_on      = 1'b1; // 블링크 플래그 

    always @(posedge clk_2Mhz) begin
        if (blink_counter == 49'hFFFFF) begin
            blink_counter <= 0;
            if (i_mode == 2'b01 || i_mode == 2'b10 || i_mode == 2'b11) begin
                display_on <= ~display_on; // 시간설정 / 알람설정/ 타이머설정에서는 디스플레이를 깜박이도록 설정
            end
        end else begin
            blink_counter <= blink_counter + 1'b1;
        end
    end
     always @(posedge clk_disp_speed) begin
        if (i_mode == 2'b01 || i_mode == 2'b10) begin   // 시계 설정 모드와 알람 설정 모드
            case (i_position)
                2'b00: begin
                    // 초 디스플레이) 십의 자리와 일의 자리 블링크
                    if (display_on) begin
                        case (cnt_seg_enb)
                            4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                            4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                            4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                            4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                            4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                            4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                        endcase
                    end else begin
                        // 블링크가 꺼진 경우
                        case (cnt_seg_enb)
                            4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                            4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                            4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                            4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                            4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                            4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                        endcase
                    end
                end
                2'b01: begin
                    // 분 디스플레이) 십의 자리와 일의 자리 블링크
                    if (display_on) begin
                        case (cnt_seg_enb)
                            4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                            4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                            4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                            4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                            4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                            4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                        endcase
                    end else begin
                        // 블링크가 꺼진 경우
                        case (cnt_seg_enb)
                            4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                            4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                            4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                            4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                            4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                            4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                        endcase
                    end
                end
                2'b10: begin
                    // 시 디스플레이) 십의 자리와 일의 자리 블링크
                    if (display_on) begin
                        case (cnt_seg_enb)
                            4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                            4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                            4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                            4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                            4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                            4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                        endcase
                    end else begin
                    // 블링크가 꺼진 경우
                        case (cnt_seg_enb)
                            4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                            4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                            4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                            4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                            4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                            4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                        endcase
                    end
                end
            endcase
        end else if (i_mode== 2'b11) begin  //타이머 모드
            if(i_timer_mode == 1'b1) begin  //timer on (블링크 동작 X)
                case (cnt_seg_enb)
                    4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                    4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                    4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                    4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                    4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                    4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                endcase
            end else  begin   //timer off
                case (i_position)
                    2'b00: begin
                        // 초 디스플레이) 십의 자리와 일의 자리 블링크
                        if (display_on) begin
                            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                            endcase
                        end else begin
                            // 블링크가 꺼진 경우
                            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                            endcase
                        end
                    end
                    2'b01: begin
                        // 분 디스플레이) 십의 자리와 일의 자리 블링크
                        if (display_on) begin
                            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                            endcase
                        end else begin
                            // 블링크가 꺼진 경우
                            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                            endcase
                        end
                    end
                    2'b10: begin
                        // 시 디스플레이) 십의 자리와 일의 자리 블링크
                        if (display_on) begin
                            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                            endcase
                        end else begin
                        // 블링크가 꺼진 경우
                            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
                            endcase
                        end
                    end
                endcase            
            end
        end else if (i_mode == 2'b00) begin // 시계 모드 (mode 0)일 때, 블링크 적용 X
            case (cnt_seg_enb)
                4'd0:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111110, i_six_seg[0*7+6:0*7], i_six_seg_dp[0]};
                4'd1:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111101, i_six_seg[1*7+6:1*7], i_six_seg_dp[1]};
                4'd2:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b111011, i_six_seg[2*7+6:2*7], i_six_seg_dp[2]};
                4'd3:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b110111, i_six_seg[3*7+6:3*7], i_six_seg_dp[3]};
                4'd4:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b101111, i_six_seg[4*7+6:4*7], i_six_seg_dp[4]};
                4'd5:   {o_seg_enb, o_seg, o_seg_dp} <= {6'b011111, i_six_seg[5*7+6:5*7], i_six_seg_dp[5]};
            endcase
        end
    end
endmodule

module dec_to_seg(
    output reg  [6:0]   o_seg,
    input       [3:0]   i_num
);
    always @(*) begin
        case (i_num)
            4'd0: o_seg = 7'b111_1110;
            4'd1: o_seg = 7'b011_0000;
            4'd2: o_seg = 7'b110_1101;
            4'd3: o_seg = 7'b111_1001;
            4'd4: o_seg = 7'b011_0011;
            4'd5: o_seg = 7'b101_1011;
            4'd6: o_seg = 7'b101_1111;
            4'd7: o_seg = 7'b111_0000;
            4'd8: o_seg = 7'b111_1111;
            4'd9: o_seg = 7'b111_0011;
            4'd10: o_seg = 7'b111_0111;
            4'd11: o_seg = 7'b001_1111;
            4'd12: o_seg = 7'b100_1110;
            4'd13: o_seg = 7'b011_1101;
            4'd14: o_seg = 7'b100_1111;
            4'd15: o_seg = 7'b100_0111;
            default:o_seg = 7'b000_0000;
        endcase
    end
endmodule

module num_split#(
    parameter RANGE = 60 
)(
    output  [3:0]               o_digit_l,
    output  [3:0]               o_digit_r,
    input   [$clog2(RANGE)-1:0] i_num
);
    assign o_digit_l = i_num/10;
    assign o_digit_r = i_num%10;
endmodule

module switch_debounce(
    output      [7:0]   o_sw,
    input       [7:0]   i_sw,
    input               i_clk,
    input               i_rstn
);
    `ifdef DEBUG
        localparam NCO_DEBOUNCE = 4;
    `else
        localparam NCO_DEBOUNCE = 1000000;
    `endif
    wire                clk_debounce;
    nco u_nco_clk_slow(
        .o_clk      (clk_debounce ),
        .i_num      (NCO_DEBOUNCE ),
        .i_clk      (i_clk        ),
        .i_rstn     (i_rstn       ));
    reg         [7:0]   dly_sw0;
    reg         [7:0]   dly_sw1;
    always @(posedge clk_debounce) begin
        dly_sw0 <= i_sw;
        dly_sw1 <= dly_sw0;
    end
    
    assign      o_sw = dly_sw0 | ~dly_sw1;
endmodule

module hms_cnt(
    output reg  [5:0]   o_hms_cnt,
    output reg          o_max_hit, //1 or 0
    input       [5:0]   i_max_cnt, //59
    input               i_direct,
    input               i_clk,
    input               i_rstn
);
    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_hms_cnt <= 6'd0;
            o_max_hit <= 1'b0;
        end else begin
            if (i_direct==0) begin //i_direct=0 : upcnt
                if(o_hms_cnt >= i_max_cnt) begin
                    o_hms_cnt <= 0;
                    o_max_hit <= 1'b1;
                end else begin
                    o_hms_cnt <= o_hms_cnt + 1;
                    o_max_hit <= 1'b0;
                end
            end else begin  //i_direct=1 : dwcnt
                 if(o_hms_cnt == 0) begin
                    o_hms_cnt <= i_max_cnt; // 다시 59로 설정
                    o_max_hit <= 1'b0;
                end else begin
                    o_hms_cnt <= o_hms_cnt - 1;
                    o_max_hit <= 1'b0;
                end
            end
        end
    end
endmodule

module hms_cnt_timer(
    output reg  [5:0]   o_hms_cnt_timer,
    output reg          o_timer_max_hit, //1 or 0

    input       [5:0]   i_timer_max_cnt, //59
    input               i_timer_mode,
    input               i_direct,
    input               i_clk,
    input               i_rstn
);

    localparam MODE_TIMER_START = 1'b1;    // 타이머 동작 시작 (blink 멈춤)
    localparam MODE_TIMER_SETTING = 1'b0; // 타이머 시간 설정 (up/down 둘 다 가능)
    

    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_hms_cnt_timer <= 6'd0;
            o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b0;
        end else begin
            if (i_timer_mode == MODE_TIMER_SETTING )begin
                if(i_direct == 0) begin    //upcnt
                    if(o_hms_cnt_timer >= i_timer_max_cnt) begin
                        o_hms_cnt_timer <= 6'd0;
                        o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b1;
                    end else begin 
                        o_hms_cnt_timer <= o_hms_cnt_timer +1;      
                        o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b0;   
                    end
                end else begin  //dwcnt
                    if(o_hms_cnt_timer <= 6'd0) begin
                        o_hms_cnt_timer <= i_timer_max_cnt;
                        o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b1;
                    end else begin
                        o_hms_cnt_timer <= o_hms_cnt_timer - 1;
                        o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b0;
                    end
                end
            end else if (i_timer_mode == MODE_TIMER_START) begin 
                if (o_hms_cnt_timer <= 6'd0)begin
                        o_hms_cnt_timer <= i_timer_max_cnt;
                        o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b1;
                    end else begin
                        o_hms_cnt_timer <= o_hms_cnt_timer - 6'd1;
                        o_timer_max_hit <= 1'b0;
                    end
                end
            end
        end
endmodule

module controller(
    output reg [1:0] o_mode,
    output reg [1:0] o_position,
    output reg       o_timer_mode,
    output reg       o_direct,

    output reg       o_alarm_en,
    output reg       o_timer_en,

    output reg       o_sec_cnt_clk,
    output reg       o_min_cnt_clk,
    output reg       o_hour_cnt_clk,

    output reg       o_sec_alm_clk,
    output reg       o_min_alm_clk,
    output reg       o_hour_alm_clk,

    output reg       o_sec_timer_clk,
    output reg       o_min_timer_clk,
    output reg       o_hour_timer_clk,

    input   [5:0]   i_timer_sec,
    input   [5:0]   i_timer_min,
    input   [4:0]   i_timer_hour,

    input i_timer_finish,
    input i_sec_max_hit,
    input i_min_max_hit,

    input i_sec_timer_max_hit,
    input i_min_timer_max_hit,
    input i_hour_timer_max_hit,

    input   [7:0]   i_signal_data,
    //input           i_sec_max_hit,
    //input           i_min_max_hit,
    input           [7:0] i_sw,
    input           i_clk,
    input           i_rstn
    );

    localparam MODE_CLOCK = 2'b00;
    localparam MODE_SETUP = 2'b01;
    localparam MODE_ALARM = 2'b10;
    localparam MODE_TIMER = 2'b11; //추가
     
    localparam POS_SEC      = 2'b00;
    localparam POS_MIN      = 2'b01;
    localparam POS_HOUR     = 2'b10 ;

    localparam MODE_TIMER_SETTING = 1'b0;
    localparam MODE_TIMER_START   = 1'b1;
    localparam MODE_TIMER_FINISH  = 1'b1; 

    wire [7:0] i_sig_data;

    assign i_sig_data[0]=i_signal_data[0]&&i_sw[0];  //모드변환
    assign i_sig_data[1]=i_signal_data[1]&&i_sw[1];  //시분초 바꿈
    assign i_sig_data[2]=i_signal_data[2]&&i_sw[2];  //증가
    assign i_sig_data[3]=i_signal_data[3]&&i_sw[3];  //알람 on/off
    assign i_sig_data[4]=i_signal_data[4]&&i_sw[4];  //타이머 on/off
    assign i_sig_data[7]=i_signal_data[7]&&i_sw[7];  //i_direct에 해당하는 신호

    //모드(시계/시간 설정/알람 설정/타이머 설정)선택 스위치
     always @(posedge ~i_sig_data[0] or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_mode <= MODE_CLOCK;
        end else begin
            if(o_mode != MODE_ALARM) begin
                o_mode <= o_mode + 1;
            end else if (o_mode != MODE_TIMER) begin
                o_mode <= o_mode + 1;
            end else begin
            o_mode <= MODE_CLOCK;
            end
        end
     end

    //위치(시/분/초) 조절 스위치
     always @(posedge ~i_sig_data[1] or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_position <= POS_SEC;
        end else begin
            if(o_position == POS_MIN) begin
                o_position <= POS_HOUR;
            end else if(o_position == POS_HOUR) begin
                o_position <= POS_SEC;
            end else begin
                o_position <= o_position + 1;
            end
        end
     end
    
    //알람 on/off 스위치
     always @(posedge ~i_sig_data[3] or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_alarm_en <= 0;
        end else begin
            o_alarm_en <= o_alarm_en + 1;
        end
     end

    //타이머 on/off 스위치
    always @(posedge ~i_sig_data[4] or negedge i_rstn or posedge i_timer_finish) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_timer_mode <= MODE_TIMER_SETTING;
        end else if (i_timer_finish == MODE_TIMER_FINISH) begin
            o_timer_mode <= MODE_TIMER_SETTING;
            o_timer_en <= 1'b1;
        end else if((i_timer_sec == 6'd0) && (i_timer_min == 6'd0) && (i_timer_hour == 6'd0)) begin
            o_timer_mode <= MODE_TIMER_SETTING;
            o_timer_en <= 1'b1;
        end else begin
            o_timer_mode <= o_timer_mode + 1'b1;
            o_timer_en <= 1'b1;
        end
    end

     // i_direct(upcnt/downcnt) 스위치
    always @(posedge ~i_sig_data[7] or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_direct <= 0;
        end else begin
            o_direct <= o_direct + 1;
        end
    end

     `ifdef DEBUG
        localparam NCO_NUM_1HZ = 4;
     `else
        localparam NCO_NUM_1HZ = 50000000;
     `endif

     wire clk_1hz;
     nco u_nco_clk_1hz(
        .o_clk (clk_1hz ),
        .i_num (NCO_NUM_1HZ ),
        .i_clk (i_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    always @(*) begin
        case(o_mode)
            MODE_CLOCK : begin
                o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
            end
            MODE_SETUP : begin
                case(o_position)
                    POS_SEC : begin
                        o_sec_cnt_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                        o_min_cnt_clk = 1'b0;
                        o_hour_cnt_clk = 1'b0;
                        o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                        o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                    end
                    POS_MIN : begin
                        o_sec_cnt_clk = 1'b0;
                        o_min_cnt_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                        o_hour_cnt_clk <= 1'b0;
                        o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                        o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                    end
                    POS_HOUR : begin
                        o_sec_cnt_clk <= 1'b0;
                        o_min_cnt_clk <= 1'b0;
                        o_hour_cnt_clk <= ~i_sig_data[2];
                        o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                        o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                    end
                endcase
            end
            MODE_ALARM : begin
                case(o_position)
                    POS_SEC : begin
                        o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                        o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                        o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                        o_sec_alm_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                        o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                        o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                    end
                    POS_MIN : begin
                        o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                        o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                        o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                        o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_min_alm_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                        o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                        o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                    end
                     POS_HOUR : begin
                        o_sec_cnt_clk <= clk_1hz;
                        o_min_cnt_clk <= i_sec_max_hit;
                        o_hour_cnt_clk <= i_min_max_hit;
                        o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_alm_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                        o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                        o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                        o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                    end
                endcase
            end
            MODE_TIMER : begin
                if(o_timer_mode == MODE_TIMER_START) begin
                // Timer Clock ongoing not to finish(not 00:00:00)
                if(i_timer_finish != MODE_TIMER_FINISH)begin
                    o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                    o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                    o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                    o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_sec_timer_clk = clk_1hz;
                    o_min_timer_clk = i_sec_timer_max_hit;
                    o_hour_timer_clk = i_min_timer_max_hit;
                // Timer Clock finish(00:00:00)  --> TIEMR_SETTING
                end else begin
                    o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                    o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                    o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                    o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                    o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                end
            end else begin
            case(o_position)
                POS_SEC : begin
                    o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                    o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                    o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                    o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_sec_timer_clk = ~i_sig_data[2]; 
                    o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                end
                POS_MIN : begin
                    o_sec_cnt_clk = clk_1hz;
                    o_min_cnt_clk = i_sec_max_hit;
                    o_hour_cnt_clk = i_min_max_hit;
                    o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                    o_min_timer_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                    o_hour_timer_clk = 0;
                end
                 POS_HOUR : begin
                    o_sec_cnt_clk <= clk_1hz;
                    o_min_cnt_clk <= i_sec_max_hit;
                    o_hour_cnt_clk <= i_min_max_hit;
                    o_sec_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_min_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_alm_clk = 0;
                    o_sec_timer_clk = 0; 
                    o_min_timer_clk = 0;
                    o_hour_timer_clk = ~i_sig_data[2];
                end
            endcase
            end
        end
        endcase
    end
endmodule


module minsec( 
    output reg o_alarm,
    output reg o_timer,
    output reg o_timer_finish,

    output reg [5:0] o_sec,
    output reg [5:0] o_min,
    output reg [5:0] o_hour,

    output o_sec_max_hit,
    output o_min_max_hit,

    output o_sec_timer_max_hit,
    output o_min_timer_max_hit,
    output o_hour_timer_max_hit,

    output  [5:0] sec_timer,
    output  [5:0] min_timer,
    output  [5:0] hour_timer,

    output reg [5:0] o_sec_alm,
    output reg [5:0] o_min_alm,
    output reg [5:0] o_hour_alm,

    input [1:0] i_mode,
    input i_timer_mode,

    input i_alarm_en,
    input i_timer_en,

    input i_sec_cnt_clk,
    input i_min_cnt_clk,
    input i_hour_cnt_clk,

    input i_sec_alm_clk,
    input i_min_alm_clk,
    input i_hour_alm_clk,

    input i_sec_timer_clk,
    input i_min_timer_clk,
    input i_hour_timer_clk,
    input i_clk,
    input i_direct,
    input i_rstn
    );
    
    localparam MODE_CLOCK = 2'b00;
    localparam MODE_SETUP = 2'b01;
    localparam MODE_ALARM = 2'b10;
    localparam MODE_TIMER = 2'b11;

    localparam POS_SEC = 2'b00;
    localparam POS_MIN = 2'b01;
    localparam POS_HOUR =2'b10;

    localparam MODE_TIMER_SETTING = 1'b0;
    localparam MODE_TIMER_START   = 1'b1;
    localparam MODE_TIMER_FINISH  = 1'b1;

    wire [5:0] sec_cnt;
    wire [5:0] min_cnt;
    wire [5:0] hour_cnt;

    wire [5:0] sec_alm;
    wire [5:0] min_alm;
    wire [5:0] hour_alm;

//    wire [5:0] sec_timer;
//    wire [5:0] min_timer;
//    wire [5:0] hour_timer;
//   

    hms_cnt u_hms_cnt_sec(
        .o_hms_cnt (sec_cnt ),
        .o_max_hit (o_sec_max_hit ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_max_cnt (6'd59 ),
        .i_clk (i_sec_cnt_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt u_hms_cnt_min(
        .o_hms_cnt (min_cnt ),
        .o_max_hit (o_min_max_hit ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_max_cnt (6'd59 ),
        .i_clk (i_min_cnt_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt u_hms_cnt_hour(
        .o_hms_cnt (hour_cnt ),
        .o_max_hit ( ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_max_cnt (6'd23 ),
        .i_clk (i_hour_cnt_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt u_hms_alm_sec(
        .o_hms_cnt (sec_alm ),
        .o_max_hit ( ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_max_cnt (6'd59 ),
        .i_clk (i_sec_alm_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt u_hms_alm_min(
        .o_hms_cnt (min_alm ),
        .o_max_hit ( ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_max_cnt (6'd59 ),
        .i_clk (i_min_alm_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt u_hms_alm_hour(
        .o_hms_cnt (hour_alm ),
        .o_max_hit ( ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_max_cnt (6'd23 ),
        .i_clk (i_hour_alm_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt_timer u_hms_timer_sec(
        .o_hms_cnt_timer (sec_timer ),
        .o_timer_max_hit (o_sec_timer_max_hit ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_timer_max_cnt (6'd59 ),
        .i_timer_mode (i_timer_mode ),
        .i_clk (i_sec_timer_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt_timer u_hms_timer_min(
        .o_hms_cnt_timer (min_timer ),
        .o_timer_max_hit (o_min_timer_max_hit ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_timer_max_cnt (6'd59 ),
        .i_timer_mode (i_timer_mode ),
        .i_clk (i_min_timer_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    hms_cnt_timer u_hms_timer_hour(
        .o_hms_cnt_timer (hour_timer ),
        .o_timer_max_hit ( ),
        .i_direct  (i_direct),
        .i_timer_max_cnt (6'd23 ),
        .i_timer_mode (i_timer_mode ),
        .i_clk (i_hour_timer_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn )); 

    always@(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn)begin
        //Initialization
        if(i_rstn == 1'b0)begin //!i_rstn
            o_timer_finish <= 1'b0;
        end else begin
            //@olny TIMER_START, 00:00:00 is timer_finish
            if((sec_timer==6'd0)&&(min_timer==6'd0)&&(hour_timer==6'd0) &&(i_timer_mode==MODE_TIMER_START))begin
                  o_timer_finish <= 1'b1;
            //ex) TIEMR_SETTING, 00:00:00 is not timer_finish
            end else begin
                  o_timer_finish <= 1'b0;
            end
        end
    end

    always @(*) begin
        case(i_mode)
            MODE_CLOCK: begin
                o_sec = sec_cnt;
                o_min = min_cnt;
                o_hour = hour_cnt;
            end
            MODE_SETUP: begin
                o_sec = sec_cnt;
                o_min = min_cnt;
                o_hour = hour_cnt;
            end
            MODE_ALARM: begin
                o_sec = sec_alm;
                o_min = min_alm;
                o_hour = hour_alm;
            end
            MODE_TIMER: begin
                o_sec = sec_timer;
                o_min = min_timer;
                o_hour = hour_timer;
            end
        endcase
    end

    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_alarm <= 0;
        end else begin
            if( (sec_cnt== sec_alm) && (min_cnt== min_alm) && (hour_cnt== hour_alm)) begin
                o_alarm <= 1 && i_alarm_en;
            end else begin
                o_alarm <= o_alarm && i_alarm_en;
            end
        end
    end
    //00.00.00초 일 때 알람 울리도록 설정
    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            o_timer <= 0;
        end else begin
            if( (sec_timer == 6'd0) && (min_timer == 6'd0) && (hour_timer == 6'd0) && (i_timer_mode == MODE_TIMER_START)) begin
                o_timer <= 1 & i_timer_en;
            end else begin
                o_timer <= o_timer & i_timer_en;
            end
        end
    end
endmodule

//    always @(*) begin
//        o_sec_alm = sec_alm;
//        o_min_alm = min_alm;
//        o_hour_alm = hour_alm;
//    end

module buzz(
    output o_buzz,
    input i_buzz_en,
    input i_clk,
    input i_rstn
);
    localparam C = 191113;
    localparam D = 170262;
    localparam E = 151686;
    localparam F = 143173;
    localparam G = 127552;
    localparam GS = 120394;
    localparam A = 113636;
    localparam B = 101238;
    
    localparam HC = 95556;
    localparam HD = 85131;
    localparam HDS = 80353;
    localparam HE = 75843;
 
    localparam N = 1000;

    wire            clk_beat;
    nco         u_nco_beat(
        .o_clk          (clk_beat   ),
        .i_num          (25000000   ),
        .i_clk          (i_clk      ),
        .i_rstn         (i_rstn     ));  

    reg [5:0] cnt_buzz;

    always @ (posedge clk_beat or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
           cnt_buzz <= 6'd0;
        end else begin
           if (i_buzz_en) begin
              if(cnt_buzz == 6'd48) begin
                 cnt_buzz <= 6'd0;
              end else begin
                 cnt_buzz <= cnt_buzz + 1'd1;
              end
           end
        end
    end

    reg [31:0] buzz_freq;
    always@(*)begin
        case(cnt_buzz)
            6'd00: buzz_freq = HE ;
            6'd01: buzz_freq = HDS ;
            6'd02: buzz_freq = HE ;
            6'd03: buzz_freq = HDS ;
            6'd04: buzz_freq = HE ;
            6'd05: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd06: buzz_freq = HD ;
            6'd07: buzz_freq = HC ;
            6'd08: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd09: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd10: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd11: buzz_freq = N ;

            6'd12: buzz_freq = C ;
            6'd13: buzz_freq = E ;
            6'd14: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd15: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd16: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd17: buzz_freq = B ;
            
            6'd18: buzz_freq = E ;
            6'd19: buzz_freq = GS ;
            6'd20: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd21: buzz_freq = HC ;
            6'd22: buzz_freq = HC;
            6'd23: buzz_freq = HC ;
            
            
            6'd24: buzz_freq = E ;
            6'd25: buzz_freq = HE ;
            6'd26: buzz_freq = HDS ;
            6'd27: buzz_freq = HE ;
            6'd28: buzz_freq = HDS ;
            6'd29: buzz_freq = HE ;
            6'd30: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd31: buzz_freq = HD ;
            6'd32: buzz_freq = HC ;
            6'd33: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd34: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd35: buzz_freq = A ;
            
            6'd36: buzz_freq = C ;
            6'd37: buzz_freq = E ;
            6'd38: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd39: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd40: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd41: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd42: buzz_freq = E ;
            6'd43: buzz_freq = HC ;
            6'd44: buzz_freq = B ;
            6'd45: buzz_freq = A ;
            6'd46: buzz_freq = A;
            6'd47: buzz_freq = A ;
        endcase
    end
    wire buzz;
    nco u_nco_buzz(
        .o_clk (buzz ),
        .i_num (buzz_freq ),
        .i_clk (i_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn ));
    assign o_buzz = buzz & i_buzz_en;
endmodule

module text_lcd(
    output reg                  o_lcd_e,
    output reg                  o_lcd_rs,
    output reg                  o_lcd_rw,
    inout       [7:0]           io_lcd_data,
    input       [2*16*8-1:0]    i_line_data,
    input                       i_line_data_valid,
    input                       i_clk,
    input                       i_rstn
);

// 10bits: RS & R/W & Data(8-bits)
    localparam CMD_CLEAR_DISPLAY        = 10'b00_0000_0001;
    localparam CMD_RETURN_HOME          = 10'b00_0000_0010;
    localparam CMD_ENTRY_MODE_SET       = 10'b00_0000_0110;
    localparam CMD_DISP_ONOFF_CTRL      = 10'b00_0000_1100;
    localparam CMD_CURSOR_DISP_SHIFT    = 10'b00_0001_1000;
    localparam CMD_FUNCTION_SET         = 10'b00_0011_1100;
    localparam CMD_READ_BUSY_FLAG       = 10'b01_zzzz_zzzz;
    localparam CMD_SET_DDRAM_ADDR1      = 10'b00_1000_0000;
    localparam CMD_SET_DDRAM_ADDR2      = 10'b00_1100_0000;
    localparam CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA       = 2'b10;

    `ifdef DEBUG
        reg     [127:0]         state;  // 8bit * 16글자 (1line)
        localparam IDLE         = "IDLE";
        localparam WAIT_INPUT   = "WAIT_INPUT";
        localparam BUSY_CHECK   = "BUSY_CHECK";
        localparam EXCUTE_CMD   = "EXCUTE_CMD";
    `else
        reg     [1:0]           state;
        localparam IDLE         = 2'b00;
        localparam WAIT_INPUT   = 2'b01;
        localparam BUSY_CHECK   = 2'b10;
        localparam EXCUTE_CMD   = 2'b11;
    `endif
        
    reg [2*16*8-1:0] line_data;
    always @(posedge i_clk or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            line_data <= 0;
        end else begin
            if(i_line_data_valid) begin
                line_data <= i_line_data;   // 데이터 할당
            end else begin
                line_data <= line_data;     // 기존 데이터 그대로
            end
        end
    end

    wire clk_1mhz;
    nco u_nco(
        .o_clk          (clk_1mhz       ),
        .i_num          (50             ),
        .i_clk          (i_clk          ),
        .i_rstn         (i_rstn         ));

    reg                 out_en;
    reg     [7:0]       lcd_data;
    assign              io_lcd_data = out_en? lcd_data : 8'hzz; //busy flag 읽는 용도
    
    reg     [1:0]       cnt_timing;
    reg     [7:0]       cnt_cmd;
    reg                 busy_flag;
    
    always @(posedge clk_1mhz or negedge i_rstn) begin  //제어용 Clock
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            cnt_timing <= 0;
        end else begin
            cnt_timing <= cnt_timing + 1;   //0,1,2,3 무한반복 
        end
    end

    always @(posedge clk_1mhz or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            state <= IDLE;
            cnt_cmd <= 0;
            busy_flag <= 1;
        end else begin
            if(cnt_timing == 3) begin   //timing이 3일 때 state 변화
                case(state)
                    IDLE: begin
                        if(i_line_data_valid) begin
                            state <= WAIT_INPUT;
                        end else begin
                            state <= IDLE;
                        end
                    end

                    WAIT_INPUT: state <= BUSY_CHECK;
                    BUSY_CHECK: begin
                        if(busy_flag == 0) begin
                            state <= EXCUTE_CMD;
                        end else begin
                            state <= BUSY_CHECK;
                        end
                    end
                    EXCUTE_CMD: begin
                        if({o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} == CMD_RETURN_HOME) begin
                            state <= IDLE;
                            cnt_cmd <= 0;
                        end else begin
                            state <= BUSY_CHECK;
                            cnt_cmd <= cnt_cmd + 1;
                        end
                    end
                endcase
            end else begin
                if(state == BUSY_CHECK) begin
                    busy_flag <= io_lcd_data[7];
                end
            end
        end
    end


    always @(*) begin
        if(state == BUSY_CHECK) begin
            out_en = 0;
        end else begin
            out_en = 1;
        end
    end

    always @(*) begin
        if(cnt_timing == 1 || cnt_timing == 2) begin
            o_lcd_e = 1;
        end else begin
            o_lcd_e = 0;
        end
    end

    always @(*) begin
        case(state)
            BUSY_CHECK: begin
            {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_READ_BUSY_FLAG;
            end
            EXCUTE_CMD: begin
                case(cnt_cmd)
                00: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_CLEAR_DISPLAY;
                01: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_FUNCTION_SET;
                02: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_DISP_ONOFF_CTRL;
                03: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_ENTRY_MODE_SET;
                04: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_SET_DDRAM_ADDR1;
                05: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-00*8)-:8]};
                06: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-01*8)-:8]};
                07: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-02*8)-:8]};
                08: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-03*8)-:8]};
                09: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-04*8)-:8]};
                10: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-05*8)-:8]};
                11: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-06*8)-:8]};
                12: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-07*8)-:8]};
                13: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-08*8)-:8]};
                14: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-09*8)-:8]};
                15: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-10*8)-:8]};
                16: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-11*8)-:8]};
                17: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-12*8)-:8]};
                18: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-13*8)-:8]};
                19: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-14*8)-:8]};
                20: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-15*8)-:8]};
                21: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_SET_DDRAM_ADDR2;
                22: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-16*8)-:8]};
                23: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-17*8)-:8]};
                24: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-18*8)-:8]};
                25: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-19*8)-:8]};
                26: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-20*8)-:8]};
                27: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-21*8)-:8]};
                28: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-22*8)-:8]};
                29: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-23*8)-:8]};
                30: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-24*8)-:8]};
                31: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-25*8)-:8]};
                32: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-26*8)-:8]};
                33: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-27*8)-:8]};
                34: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-28*8)-:8]};
                35: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-29*8)-:8]};
                36: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-30*8)-:8]};
                37: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = {CMD_WRITE_RAM_DATA, line_data[(2*16*8-1-31*8)-:8]};
                38: {o_lcd_rs, o_lcd_rw, lcd_data} = CMD_RETURN_HOME;
                endcase
            end
        endcase
    end
endmodule

module dec_to_lcd(
   output reg [7:0] o_lcd,
   input      [3:0] i_num
);

    always @(*) begin
        case(i_num)
            4'd0:    o_lcd = 8'd48;
            4'd1:    o_lcd = 8'd49;
            4'd2:    o_lcd = 8'd50;
            4'd3:    o_lcd = 8'd51;
            4'd4:    o_lcd = 8'd52;
            4'd5:    o_lcd = 8'd53;
            4'd6:    o_lcd = 8'd54;
            4'd7:    o_lcd = 8'd55;
            4'd8:    o_lcd = 8'd56;
            4'd9:    o_lcd = 8'd57;
            default: o_lcd = 8'd48;
        endcase
    end

endmodule


module text_lcd_setup(
   output reg  [2*16*8-1:0]    line_data,
   output reg                  line_data_valid,
   input   [5:0]               i_alarm_sec,
   input   [5:0]               i_alarm_min,
   input   [5:0]               i_alarm_hour,
   input       [1:0]           i_mode,
   input                       i_alarm_en,
   input       [1:0]           i_position,
   input                       i_clk,
   input                       i_rstn
);




    localparam CHAR_SPACE = 8'd20;
    localparam CHAR_DOT = 8'd46;
    localparam CHAR_PLUS = 8'd43;
    localparam CHAR_CMM_U = 8'd39;
    localparam CHAR_CMM_B = 8'd44;
    localparam CHAR_COLON = 8'd58;
    localparam CHAR_COMMA = 8'd39;
    localparam CHAR_SLASH = 8'd47;
    localparam CHAR_A = 8'd65;
    localparam CHAR_B = 8'd66;
    localparam CHAR_C = 8'd67;
    localparam CHAR_D = 8'd68;
    localparam CHAR_E = 8'd69;
    localparam CHAR_F = 8'd70;
    localparam CHAR_H = 8'd72;
    localparam CHAR_S = 8'd83;
    localparam CHAR_T = 8'd84;
    localparam CHAR_R = 8'd82;
    localparam CHAR_O = 8'd79;
    localparam CHAR_P = 8'd80;
    localparam CHAR_K = 8'd75;
    localparam CHAR_M = 8'd77;
    localparam CHAR_Y = 8'd89;
    localparam CHAR_U = 8'd85;
    localparam CHAR_N = 8'd78;
    localparam CHAR_G = 8'd71;
    localparam CHAR_W = 8'd87;
    localparam CHAR_I = 8'd73;
    localparam CHAR_V = 8'd86;
    localparam CHAR_L = 8'd76;
    localparam CHAR_Z = 8'd90;


    localparam      RANGE1       = 60;
    localparam      RANGE2       = 24;


    wire   [3:0]   o_digit_lcd_s_l;
    wire   [3:0]   o_digit_lcd_s_r;
    wire   [3:0]   o_digit_lcd_m_l;
    wire   [3:0]   o_digit_lcd_m_r;
    wire   [3:0]   o_digit_lcd_h_l;
    wire   [3:0]   o_digit_lcd_h_r;

    
    num_split#(
        .RANGE   (RANGE1            ))
    u_num_split_lcd_sec(
        .o_digit_l (o_digit_lcd_s_l ),
        .o_digit_r (o_digit_lcd_s_r ),
        .i_num     (i_alarm_sec     ));


    num_split#(
        .RANGE   (RANGE1            )) 
    u_num_split_lcd_min(
        .o_digit_l (o_digit_lcd_m_l ),
        .o_digit_r (o_digit_lcd_m_r ),
        .i_num     (i_alarm_min     ));

    
    num_split#(
        .RANGE   (RANGE2           ))
    u_num_split_lcd_hour(
        .o_digit_l (o_digit_lcd_h_l ),
        .o_digit_r (o_digit_lcd_h_r ),
        .i_num     (i_alarm_hour    ));

   //hour
    wire   [7:0]      hour_lcd_l;
    dec_to_lcd      u_dec_to_lcd_hour_l(
        .o_lcd         (hour_lcd_l       ),
        .i_num         (o_digit_lcd_h_l));   

    wire   [7:0]      hour_lcd_r;
    dec_to_lcd      u_dec_to_lcd_hour_r(
        .o_lcd         (hour_lcd_r      ),
        .i_num         (o_digit_lcd_h_r));      

   //minute
    wire   [7:0]      min_lcd_l;
    dec_to_lcd      u_dec_to_lcd_min_l(
        .o_lcd         (min_lcd_l       ),
        .i_num         (o_digit_lcd_m_l ));      

    wire   [7:0]      min_lcd_r;
    dec_to_lcd      u_dec_to_lcd_min_r(
        .o_lcd         (min_lcd_r      ),
        .i_num         (o_digit_lcd_m_r));   
    
    //second
    wire   [7:0]      sec_lcd_l;
    dec_to_lcd      u_dec_to_lcd_sec_l(
        .o_lcd         (sec_lcd_l       ),
        .i_num         (o_digit_lcd_s_l));      


    wire   [7:0]      sec_lcd_r;
    dec_to_lcd      u_dec_to_lcd_sec_r( 
        .o_lcd         (sec_lcd_r      ),
        .i_num         (o_digit_lcd_s_r));   
    
    

    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data0;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data1;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data2;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data3;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data4;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data5;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data6;
    wire [2*16*8-1:0] line_data7;
   
    assign line_data0 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_C, CHAR_L, CHAR_O, CHAR_C, CHAR_K, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, hour_lcd_l, hour_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, min_lcd_l, min_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, sec_lcd_l, sec_lcd_r, CHAR_SPACE};   // 시계 모드(알람 on-> 알람 설정 시각도 표시)
    assign line_data1 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_C, CHAR_L, CHAR_O, CHAR_C, CHAR_K, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_O, CHAR_F, CHAR_F, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE};   // 시계 모드(알람 off)
    assign line_data2 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_S, CHAR_E, CHAR_T, CHAR_U, CHAR_P, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, hour_lcd_l, hour_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, min_lcd_l, min_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, sec_lcd_l, sec_lcd_r, CHAR_SPACE};   // 시간 설정 모드 (알람 on-> 알람 설정 시각도 표시)
    assign line_data3 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_S, CHAR_E, CHAR_T, CHAR_U, CHAR_P, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_O, CHAR_F, CHAR_F, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE};   // 시간 설정 모드 (알람 off)
    assign line_data4 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, hour_lcd_l, hour_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, min_lcd_l, min_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, sec_lcd_l, sec_lcd_r, CHAR_SPACE};   // 알람 설정 모드 (알람 on -> 알람 설정 시각도 표시)
    assign line_data5 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_O, CHAR_F, CHAR_F, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE};   // 알람 설정 모드 (알람 off)
    assign line_data6 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_T, CHAR_I, CHAR_M, CHAR_E, CHAR_R, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, hour_lcd_l, hour_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, min_lcd_l, min_lcd_r, CHAR_COLON, sec_lcd_l, sec_lcd_r, CHAR_SPACE};   // 타이머 설정 모드 (알람 on -> 알람 설정 시각도 표시)
    assign line_data7 = {CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_M, CHAR_O, CHAR_D, CHAR_E, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_T, CHAR_I, CHAR_M, CHAR_E, CHAR_R, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_A, CHAR_L, CHAR_A, CHAR_R, CHAR_M, CHAR_COLON, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_O, CHAR_F, CHAR_F, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE, CHAR_SPACE};   // 타이머 설정 모드 (알람 off)

    `ifdef DEBUG
        localparam NCO_LINE_DATA = 50;
    `else
        localparam NCO_LINE_DATA =  50000000;
    `endif

    wire lcd;
    reg [20:0]  cnt;
    nco u_nco(
        .o_clk (lcd ),
        .i_num (NCO_LINE_DATA ),
        .i_clk (i_clk ),
        .i_rstn (i_rstn ));
 
    always @(posedge lcd or negedge i_rstn) begin
        if(!i_rstn) begin
            line_data <= 0;
            line_data_valid <= 0;
            cnt <= 0;
        end else begin
            if(i_mode == 2'b00) begin   // 시계 모드
                if(i_alarm_en) begin    // alarm off
                    if(cnt == 0) begin
                        line_data <= line_data0;
                        line_data_valid <= 1;
                        cnt <= cnt + 1;
                    end else if (cnt == 5) begin
                        line_data       <= 0;
                        line_data_valid <= 0;
                        cnt             <= 0;
                     end else begin
                        line_data       <= 0;
                        line_data_valid <= 0;
                        cnt <= cnt + 1;
                    end
                end else begin  // alarm on
                    if(cnt == 0) begin
                        line_data <= line_data1;
                        line_data_valid <= 1;
                        cnt <= cnt + 1;
                    end else if(cnt == 5) begin
                        line_data       <= 0;
                        line_data_valid <= 0;
                        cnt             <= 0;
                    end else begin
                        line_data       <= 0;
                        line_data_valid <= 0;
                        cnt <= cnt + 1;
                    end
                end
            end else if(i_mode == 2'b01) begin  // 시간 설정 모드
                cnt <= 0;
                if(i_alarm_en) begin    //alarm off
                    if(i_position == 2'b10) begin   // 시
                        if(cnt == 0) begin
                            line_data <= line_data2;
